Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:05.73,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}狂吠吧 交織的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說前幾天的外持山降下了數年未有的暴雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實解決了缺水問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻因為突然的暴雨 地板滲水 房屋損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分的房屋 田地及一般道路都被完全淹沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是瘟神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩只可惡的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 找到你要找的東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的出了好多難以挽回 也很讓人費解的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八房 放下他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路要我做的英式鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嘗嘗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我們不敢做出如此無禮之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有藍莓 核桃和起司口味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要核桃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍莓味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起司味的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪一種好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路 你要的點心我已經做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍的女孩子們一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了信乃再出發嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被里見先生的說教 應該一會兒就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 就拜託信乃一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午我訂的一本專業書會送到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你告訴他給我送到宿舍來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是男賓止步的女校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 信乃的話會作為妹妹進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 要我把這個親自送到宿舍去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 住了宿舍之後就會暫時見不到濱路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出也需要許可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可已經半夜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里見先生的說教真是長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意郵購這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想立刻就能讀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒蘑菇的辨別方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了就知道的藥草
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就給她送過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就送…趁誰都沒有發覺的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡啊 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心不要被人發現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次來這麼大的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有種討厭的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為全是女人的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是濱路的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是冷清的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得請莊介做了鬆餅的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 明天分給班裡的同學就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了今天會有轉學生入住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的室友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是熊谷鈴 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是濱路 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼現在才回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天遲到了一會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被說教到現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有英式鬆餅 要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆餅？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如果濱路大人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座宅子就會顯得格外冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有一位無精打采的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 濱路大人為什麼突然想去上學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便成為尾崎家的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也已經具備了足夠的聰敏與教養啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們五狐也是十分的尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是優秀的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…她有一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路想成為醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓體弱多病的兒時玩伴隨時能恢復原貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他不再承受的痛苦 她想成為一名醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到之後感到十分慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是我做的 不介意的話請多吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直一個人住在這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路能來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有一點不安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是初次住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這裡規章嚴格 又全是家世良好的千金小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊谷同學是我的室友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路實在是太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我小鈴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我們一定相處得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規章很嚴格倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要不被管理員發現 多半都不會追究的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理員？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理員叫做小早川琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出身豪門的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才色兼備很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是特別嚴厲的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 烏鴉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這麼晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路 我帶來了不好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 信乃在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後院…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 濱路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉呢 烏鴉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 濱路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你來得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 你要的書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為里見那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是信乃的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為禁止男子入內 他就不肯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是這麼耿直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃你三更半夜闖進這個地方也算是個極端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 信乃隨性就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我再叫你 你就再來見我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有下次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給里見先生添太多麻煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.82,插入曲_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半個人 半個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.32,插入曲_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.69,插入曲_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各佔一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:39.50,插入曲_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共佔小小的身軀 各佔一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.10,插入曲_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唇齒相依 唇齒相依
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:45.64,插入曲_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各佔半邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 信乃 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吃了早飯 打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小文吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來打擾你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過半夜看到一隻狗背著孩子闖進來時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃雖然暈倒了  但是好像沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搞不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該是進了女校宿舍去找青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就在那裡昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使問他詳細狀況 也問不出個所以然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是撞見女鬼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好糗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了…鬼娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼娃娃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈不是人死之後變的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶什麼的 本來就沒有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣…毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越聽越糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃你為什麼會怕幽靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明都不害怕妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是超級怕鬼的體質？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是 他們明明都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了之後還在世上遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在令人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所…所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像承認了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有蟑螂也是信乃的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意外的清純呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼樣的幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 信乃 把它畫出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披著白色的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還斜跨著一個包包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面好像繫著鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怕吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大家都聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 原來你想要娃娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旦開野 你笑的太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 要我買給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
